  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Poslednja grupa punih slogova je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ye</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yue</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yuan</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yin</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yun</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ying</span>.</p>\n<p>Takođe, zapamtite da rade kao jedinstvene, neuništive jedinice.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte izgovoriti potpune slogove, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yun</span> u različitim glasovima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">yūn</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">晕</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">yún</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">云</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">yǔn</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">允</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">yùn</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">运</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>",
